  "detailed_description": "Mr Maker 3D Level Editor is a platform game, with a level maker. Inspired by the games of the 90s, but with a touch of modernity. There are some levels ready to play, the coolest is right below.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Your Own Levels</h2>You can create your levels however you like, add blocks, traps, enemies, coins, create bridges, stairs and more. As you gain experience, you’ll experience higher, creative and challenging levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/add6c06327e381af31e60b0c287740a6.poster.avif?t=1705598827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/add6c06327e381af31e60b0c287740a6.webm?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/add6c06327e381af31e60b0c287740a6.mp4?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team Creation</h2>Increase the fun by calling friends and family to create a level together.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >History - The Magic Hammer</h2>The oldest builders in the Mr Maker 3D world. They say that there is a magic hammer, capable of building or destroying anything. But if used for evil, it can make a planet disappear.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/e9596774298db24771a0b1352bca5778.poster.avif?t=1705598827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/e9596774298db24771a0b1352bca5778.webm?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/e9596774298db24771a0b1352bca5778.mp4?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items</h2>Boomerang hammer, which will help Mr Maker to defeat enemies and collect coins from a distance. A great help!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/81860c69c46400a6c2d15aa286b66df8.poster.avif?t=1705598827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/81860c69c46400a6c2d15aa286b66df8.webm?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/81860c69c46400a6c2d15aa286b66df8.mp4?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gamepad</h2>It is more enjoyable to play using a Gamepad (Joystick).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/90185dcc1444e9023e394d23de11879a.avif?t=1705598827\" width=630 height=120 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Mr Maker 3D Level Editor is a platform game, with a level maker. Inspired by the games of the 90s, but with a touch of modernity. There are some levels ready to play, the coolest is right below.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Your Own Levels</h2>You can create your levels however you like, add blocks, traps, enemies, coins, create bridges, stairs and more. As you gain experience, you’ll experience higher, creative and challenging levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/add6c06327e381af31e60b0c287740a6.poster.avif?t=1705598827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/add6c06327e381af31e60b0c287740a6.webm?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/add6c06327e381af31e60b0c287740a6.mp4?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Team Creation</h2>Increase the fun by calling friends and family to create a level together.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >History - The Magic Hammer</h2>The oldest builders in the Mr Maker 3D world. They say that there is a magic hammer, capable of building or destroying anything. But if used for evil, it can make a planet disappear.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/e9596774298db24771a0b1352bca5778.poster.avif?t=1705598827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/e9596774298db24771a0b1352bca5778.webm?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/e9596774298db24771a0b1352bca5778.mp4?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items</h2>Boomerang hammer, which will help Mr Maker to defeat enemies and collect coins from a distance. A great help!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/81860c69c46400a6c2d15aa286b66df8.poster.avif?t=1705598827\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/81860c69c46400a6c2d15aa286b66df8.webm?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/81860c69c46400a6c2d15aa286b66df8.mp4?t=1705598827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gamepad</h2>It is more enjoyable to play using a Gamepad (Joystick).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243150/extras/90185dcc1444e9023e394d23de11879a.avif?t=1705598827\" width=630 height=120 /></span>",
